1183
00:41:38,519 --> 00:41:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] Evropa je tu,

1184
00:41:39,599 --> 00:41:41,139
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije ona toliko jedinstvena.

1185
00:41:41,139 --> 00:41:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, nije, nije.

1186
00:41:42,619 --> 00:41:44,800
[SPEAKER_00] Prilikom svake malo veće krize,

1187
00:41:44,800 --> 00:41:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] svako ode u svoj šor,

1188
00:41:46,400 --> 00:41:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] što bi rekli naši slavonci.

1189
00:41:47,880 --> 00:41:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] Je, da.

1190
00:41:48,380 --> 00:41:49,260
[SPEAKER_00] I ono,

1191
00:41:49,260 --> 00:41:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] mene recimo tu baš interesira

1192
00:41:50,659 --> 00:41:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] tvoje mišljenje.

1193
00:41:51,380 --> 00:41:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] Onda se ne moramo

1194
00:41:52,599 --> 00:41:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] ni mi kao Hrvatska

1195
00:41:53,500 --> 00:41:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] gurat negdje i davat komentare

1196
00:41:54,980 --> 00:41:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] ni tipa Plenkovića,

1197
00:41:56,019 --> 00:41:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] ni tipa Milanovića.

1198
00:41:57,039 --> 00:41:57,559
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je, slažno.

1199
00:41:57,559 --> 00:41:58,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo brinuti o sebi.

1200
00:41:58,840 --> 00:42:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] Prvenstvene osobi, slažno.

1201
00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:02,460
[SPEAKER_00] Jer, vidiš da se svi oni se povuku,

1202
00:42:02,460 --> 00:42:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] šta ćemo sad mi ostati?

1203
00:42:03,460 --> 00:42:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] Mali, statistička povješka.

1204
00:42:04,199 --> 00:42:05,400
[SPEAKER_01] Mi po tom pitanju,

1205
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,519
[SPEAKER_01] kažem, ne bi,

1206
00:42:06,519 --> 00:42:07,599
[SPEAKER_01] treba bi gledati prvenstveno

1207
00:42:07,599 --> 00:42:08,800
[SPEAKER_01] svoj interes i to je to.

1208
00:42:08,800 --> 00:42:10,139
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo Ukrajina,

1209
00:42:10,139 --> 00:42:10,900
[SPEAKER_01] već možda pričati

1210
00:42:10,900 --> 00:42:12,219
[SPEAKER_01] i mi imamo neki svoj interes.

1211
00:42:12,219 --> 00:42:13,900
[SPEAKER_01] To se radi o našoj regiji i tako dalje.

1212
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:15,079
[SPEAKER_01] neko dugoročno jase,

1213
00:42:15,079 --> 00:42:16,880
[SPEAKER_01] založen za neke stvaranje

1214
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:19,780
[SPEAKER_01] nekog savjeza

1215
00:42:19,780 --> 00:42:23,079
[SPEAKER_01] između tri umora,

1216
00:42:23,079 --> 00:42:24,420
[SPEAKER_01] Jadram Baltic, Crno more,

1217
00:42:24,420 --> 00:42:25,880
[SPEAKER_01] to su zemlje s kojima dijelimo

1218
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:27,920
[SPEAKER_01] i na neki način

1219
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:29,679
[SPEAKER_01] neku sudbinu, povijest,

1220
00:42:29,679 --> 00:42:32,739
[SPEAKER_01] pa i geopolitičke

1221
00:42:32,739 --> 00:42:33,860
[SPEAKER_01] i gospodarske interese

1222
00:42:33,860 --> 00:42:36,199
[SPEAKER_01] i tu je Ukrajina veliki ovaj faktor.

1223
00:42:36,199 --> 00:42:37,780
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, okolo ovoga,

1224
00:42:37,780 --> 00:42:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] mi ih pogotovo kao Hrvatska,

1225
00:42:39,539 --> 00:42:41,219
[SPEAKER_01] ja, tu ne možemo,

1226
00:42:41,219 --> 00:42:42,820
[SPEAKER_01] mi možemo ovako tu komentirati

1227
00:42:42,820 --> 00:42:43,420
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

1228
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:45,420
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, ne trebamo se tu previše.

1229
00:42:45,420 --> 00:42:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] To je isto moje mišljenje.

1230
00:42:48,019 --> 00:42:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] Odnosi Hrvatski sa Srbijom.

1231
00:42:52,679 --> 00:42:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] Predsjednik Srbije je nemiruje.

1232
00:42:55,119 --> 00:42:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] Dobili su Zagrebčanku,

1233
00:42:56,420 --> 00:42:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] tako zvanu.

1234
00:42:58,119 --> 00:43:00,420
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je, počeli su oboružavanca

1235
00:43:00,420 --> 00:43:01,780
[SPEAKER_01] sa raketama.

1236
00:43:01,780 --> 00:43:02,900
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je to njegov način da ostane tamo na vlasti?

1237
00:43:02,900 --> 00:43:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ja mislim da je.

1238
00:43:03,559 --> 00:43:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] Jer Srbija je postala jedan veliki

1239
00:43:06,460 --> 00:43:08,559
[SPEAKER_01] šov,

1240
00:43:08,559 --> 00:43:10,599
[SPEAKER_01] zadruga je njihov

1241
00:43:10,599 --> 00:43:12,920
[SPEAKER_01] slike i prilika.

1242
00:43:12,920 --> 00:43:15,260
[SPEAKER_01] da stanja u Srbiji,

1243
00:43:15,260 --> 00:43:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] to je jedan veliki,

1244
00:43:16,260 --> 00:43:17,099
[SPEAKER_01] kako se to kaže,

1245
00:43:17,099 --> 00:43:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] žanr,

1246
00:43:21,099 --> 00:43:25,519
[SPEAKER_01] tabloidi i tako dalje.

1247
00:43:25,519 --> 00:43:26,340
[SPEAKER_01] Žuta štamba.

1248
00:43:26,340 --> 00:43:26,940
[SPEAKER_01] Žuta štamba.

1249
00:43:26,940 --> 00:43:27,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ma ne, ono,

1250
00:43:27,800 --> 00:43:29,099
[SPEAKER_01] uglavnom, ono,

1251
00:43:29,099 --> 00:43:30,340
[SPEAKER_01] Srbiji je sve šov,

1252
00:43:30,340 --> 00:43:31,400
[SPEAKER_01] sve spektakali,

1253
00:43:31,400 --> 00:43:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] tako onda,

1254
00:43:32,019 --> 00:43:33,619
[SPEAKER_01] da bi ostale na vlasti,

1255
00:43:33,619 --> 00:43:34,760
[SPEAKER_01] morate dajte spektakali,

1256
00:43:34,760 --> 00:43:36,239
[SPEAKER_01] ne prijatelje od onih koji vam,

1257
00:43:36,239 --> 00:43:38,059
[SPEAKER_01] okej, mi je,

1258
00:43:38,059 --> 00:43:39,719
[SPEAKER_01] imamo povijeska koju imamo,

1259
00:43:39,719 --> 00:43:40,480
[SPEAKER_01] međutim,

1260
00:43:40,480 --> 00:43:42,539
[SPEAKER_01] da sad prijeti neki sukob,

1261
00:43:42,539 --> 00:43:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] naravno da ne.

1262
00:43:43,920 --> 00:43:45,260
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo to,

1263
00:43:45,260 --> 00:43:46,460
[SPEAKER_01] ja se bar nadam,

1264
00:43:46,460 --> 00:43:46,900
[SPEAKER_01] riješili,

1265
00:43:46,900 --> 00:43:47,179
[SPEAKER_01] eto,

1266
00:43:47,260 --> 00:43:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] prijatelje,

1267
00:43:47,960 --> 00:43:48,440
[SPEAKER_01] prijatelje.

1268
00:43:48,440 --> 00:43:50,260
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže da je to zbog onog saveza,

1269
00:43:50,260 --> 00:43:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] Priština, Tirana, Zagreb.

1270
00:43:51,960 --> 00:43:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da, je, da.

1271
00:43:52,539 --> 00:43:53,900
[SPEAKER_01] Savez koji nije,

1272
00:43:53,900 --> 00:43:55,500
[SPEAKER_01] savez koji nije savez,

1273
00:43:55,500 --> 00:43:57,920
[SPEAKER_01] neko je suradnja, jel da?

1274
00:43:57,920 --> 00:43:58,260
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim,

1275
00:43:58,260 --> 00:44:00,639
[SPEAKER_01] imamo određene suradnje i sa Srbijom,

1276
00:44:00,639 --> 00:44:02,219
[SPEAKER_01] pisanje prije negdje 15-a godina.

1277
00:44:02,219 --> 00:44:03,300
[SPEAKER_00] Da, već dugo i vojnu tako su.

1278
00:44:03,300 --> 00:44:04,659
[SPEAKER_00] Da, vojnu suradnju,

1279
00:44:04,659 --> 00:44:06,760
[SPEAKER_01] imamo vojnu suradnju i sa njima,

1280
00:44:06,760 --> 00:44:08,320
[SPEAKER_01] ali to iz njihove,

1281
00:44:08,320 --> 00:44:11,019
[SPEAKER_01] iz Vučićeve PR perspektive zvuči

1282
00:44:11,019 --> 00:44:11,599
[SPEAKER_01] jako dobro,

1283
00:44:11,699 --> 00:44:13,880
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo za njegovu glasaču gubazu,

1284
00:44:13,880 --> 00:44:15,480
[SPEAKER_01] koja je to starija i tako dalje,

1285
00:44:15,480 --> 00:44:16,079
[SPEAKER_01] koja ono,

1286
00:44:16,079 --> 00:44:18,380
[SPEAKER_01] i dalje živi u tom nekim bajkama

1287
00:44:18,380 --> 00:44:20,880
[SPEAKER_01] o krvočnim ustašama i tako dalje,

1288
00:44:20,880 --> 00:44:21,719
[SPEAKER_01] tako da,

1289
00:44:21,719 --> 00:44:24,760
[SPEAKER_01] s te perspektive mogu razumijet,

1290
00:44:24,760 --> 00:44:25,539
[SPEAKER_01] u smislu, znam,

1291
00:44:25,539 --> 00:44:26,619
[SPEAKER_01] očito je to,

1292
00:44:26,619 --> 00:44:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] to neki razlog zašto se to događa.

1293
00:44:29,619 --> 00:44:31,139
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, eto.

1294
00:44:31,139 --> 00:44:32,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ali moram priznati da,

1295
00:44:32,940 --> 00:44:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] recimo i njemu i plenku i čupašu

1296
00:44:35,119 --> 00:44:36,059
[SPEAKER_00] ovi svjetski sukobi,

1297
00:44:36,059 --> 00:44:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] jer tad se vlast redko mijenja.

1298
00:44:38,239 --> 00:44:39,320
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je, upravo to.

1299
00:44:39,320 --> 00:44:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je.

1300
00:44:39,960 --> 00:44:41,280
[SPEAKER_00] Tad se vlast redko mijenja

1301
00:44:41,280 --> 00:44:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] i njima je dobro.

1302
00:44:42,880 --> 00:44:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] Je.

1303
00:44:43,440 --> 00:44:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kakao je plan hrvatskih suveriste dalje

1304
00:44:46,000 --> 00:44:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] za cijelu hrvatsku?

1305
00:44:46,980 --> 00:44:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] Podružnice,

1306
00:44:48,159 --> 00:44:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] jačanje, vjerovatno,

1307
00:44:49,380 --> 00:44:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] tako.

1308
00:44:49,880 --> 00:44:50,599
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je.

1309
00:44:50,599 --> 00:44:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] Okupljanje desnici,

1310
00:44:51,619 --> 00:44:53,039
[SPEAKER_00] da smo rekli na početku, da.

1311
00:44:53,039 --> 00:44:54,179
[SPEAKER_00] Pa okupljanje desnici je nama glavni cijel.

1312
00:44:54,179 --> 00:44:55,219
[SPEAKER_00] Da će baš biti interesantno,

1313
00:44:55,219 --> 00:44:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] hoćete uspjeti to.

1314
00:44:56,019 --> 00:44:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi to, recimo,

1315
00:44:57,039 --> 00:44:58,760
[SPEAKER_00] desno-orientirano obidočko tijelo

1316
00:44:58,760 --> 00:45:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] to čekaju već desetlječima.

1317
00:45:00,000 --> 00:45:00,599
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je, je.

1318
00:45:00,599 --> 00:45:01,780
[SPEAKER_01] Iako ja moram ovako,

1319
00:45:01,780 --> 00:45:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da čak situacija na desnici

1320
00:45:04,559 --> 00:45:06,019
[SPEAKER_01] nije nikad čak bila ni bolja.

1321
00:45:06,019 --> 00:45:07,780
[SPEAKER_01] Bez obzira šta postoje različite stranke.

1322
00:45:07,780 --> 00:45:09,659
[SPEAKER_01] Sjetite se situacije pri 15 godina.

1323
00:45:09,659 --> 00:45:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] HSP imao jednog zastupnika u saboru

1324
00:45:12,619 --> 00:45:13,340
[SPEAKER_01] i to je bilo to.

1325
00:45:13,340 --> 00:45:16,619
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga je i HSP otišao van sabora

1326
00:45:16,619 --> 00:45:18,199
[SPEAKER_01] i vi niste praktički imali ništa.

1327
00:45:18,199 --> 00:45:20,559
[SPEAKER_01] Sad imamo četiri stranke u saboru

1328
00:45:20,559 --> 00:45:21,760
[SPEAKER_01] koje su tesne pravinjencije.

1329
00:45:21,760 --> 00:45:23,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ulaze dvije različite.

1330
00:45:23,159 --> 00:45:24,579
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi smo i na prošlijim izborima imali

1331
00:45:24,579 --> 00:45:25,960
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo,

1332
00:45:25,960 --> 00:45:28,780
[SPEAKER_01] s jedne strane smo bili mi suverenisti sa mostom.

1333
00:45:28,780 --> 00:45:34,260
[SPEAKER_01] S druje strane išao je domovinski pokret.

1334
00:45:34,260 --> 00:45:35,780
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, či, i svi smo ušli u sabor.

1335
00:45:35,780 --> 00:45:38,679
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, kažem, mislim da se to može

1336
00:45:38,679 --> 00:45:40,860
[SPEAKER_01] još bolje, još više.

1337
00:45:40,860 --> 00:45:44,179
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo, eto, ostvarili jako dobar uspjeh

1338
00:45:44,179 --> 00:45:45,380
[SPEAKER_01] kao suverenisti u Vukovaru.

1339
00:45:45,380 --> 00:45:47,559
[SPEAKER_01] To je čak i nas iznenadilo

1340
00:45:47,559 --> 00:45:51,400
[SPEAKER_01] s obzirom da smo išli protiv dvije vladajuće stranke

1341
00:45:51,400 --> 00:45:51,980
[SPEAKER_01] koje je tamo...

1342
00:45:51,980 --> 00:45:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] ADZ i DP.

1343
00:45:52,599 --> 00:45:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] ADZ i DP zajedno.

1344
00:45:54,000 --> 00:45:55,940
[SPEAKER_01] Naš Marijan Pavličak je uspio

1345
00:45:55,940 --> 00:46:01,500
[SPEAKER_01] dobiti tu bitku za vukovar političku

1346
00:46:01,500 --> 00:46:05,159
[SPEAKER_01] i na neki način tamo ćemo, eto,

1347
00:46:05,159 --> 00:46:07,679
[SPEAKER_01] pokušati pokazati što znamo i što možemo.

1348
00:46:07,679 --> 00:46:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, gospodin Pavličak se i povukao

1349
00:46:11,699 --> 00:46:13,320
[SPEAKER_01] svoj mandat u saboru,

1350
00:46:13,320 --> 00:46:15,900
[SPEAKER_01] dok se bavi samo i slučivo gradom,

1351
00:46:15,900 --> 00:46:17,460
[SPEAKER_01] jer to je veliki posao.

1352
00:46:17,460 --> 00:46:21,679
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, to je nešto gdje ćemo se

1353
00:46:22,039 --> 00:46:25,599
[SPEAKER_01] fokusirat, znači, gradnja, organizacija

1354
00:46:25,599 --> 00:46:29,599
[SPEAKER_01] i borba za zajedništvo na desnici.

1355
00:46:29,599 --> 00:46:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ste u Karlovcu?

1356
00:46:30,599 --> 00:46:31,380
[SPEAKER_00] Moram priznati.

1357
00:46:31,380 --> 00:46:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] U Karlovcu imamo tu,

1358
00:46:33,519 --> 00:46:35,440
[SPEAKER_01] imamo nešto članova,

1359
00:46:35,440 --> 00:46:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] članova, nismo nešto pretjereno jakim,

1360
00:46:37,960 --> 00:46:41,480
[SPEAKER_01] išli smo tu zajedno sa mostom na izbore,

1361
00:46:41,480 --> 00:46:43,679
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da je tu naš Ivan Krajcar bio,

1362
00:46:43,679 --> 00:46:44,719
[SPEAKER_01] nosili, ali ste?

1363
00:46:44,719 --> 00:46:45,300
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1364
00:46:45,300 --> 00:46:48,039
[SPEAKER_01] Nažalost, jako bili smo, ne znam,

1365
00:46:48,039 --> 00:46:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] blizu 5%, što mi je bilo jako žao,

1366
00:46:51,340 --> 00:46:53,780
[SPEAKER_01] ali idemo dalje.

1367
00:46:54,000 --> 00:46:55,719
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, eto, uglavnom,

1368
00:46:55,719 --> 00:46:59,260
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, ja se nadam da ćemo i u Karlovcu imat

1369
00:46:59,260 --> 00:47:01,920
[SPEAKER_01] jednu ovaj dobru organizaciju,

1370
00:47:01,920 --> 00:47:03,559
[SPEAKER_01] da budemo, da imamo neki rezultat,

1371
00:47:03,559 --> 00:47:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] respektabilan, tako da.

1372
00:47:06,099 --> 00:47:08,179
[SPEAKER_00] Možno pravi, spominio si i udrugu Jazovka.

1373
00:47:08,179 --> 00:47:08,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1374
00:47:08,440 --> 00:47:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] Pa možeš nešto već o tome?

1375
00:47:10,079 --> 00:47:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] Pa evo, da, ja sam već

1376
00:47:11,739 --> 00:47:14,400
[SPEAKER_01] nekde godinu i pol dana

1377
00:47:14,400 --> 00:47:15,079
[SPEAKER_01] predsjednik

1378
00:47:15,079 --> 00:47:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] udruge Hrvatski obredni iz drugi Jazovka,

1379
00:47:18,619 --> 00:47:21,719
[SPEAKER_01] uključen sam u njezini rad još od samog početaka.

1380
00:47:21,719 --> 00:47:24,019
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam puno puta

1381
00:47:24,019 --> 00:47:25,539
[SPEAKER_01] voditelj

1382
00:47:25,539 --> 00:47:27,980
[SPEAKER_01] programa, tamo autor

1383
00:47:27,980 --> 00:47:30,659
